","name":"Array.min?","line":52,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/Array/Basic.html#Array.min?","doc":"Find the first minimal element of an array. If the array is empty, `none` is\nreturned. If `start` and `stop` are given, only the subarray `xs[start:stop]` is\nconsidered.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/Array/Basic.html#Array.min?\"><span class=\"name\">Array</span>.<span class=\"name\">min?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">ord</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Ord.html#Ord\">Ord</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">xs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">start</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> := <span class=\"fn\">0</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stop</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> := <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">xs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array.size\">size</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/6a49e4c22164b1d18665837cf1e148131c7a6c4d/Batteries/Data/Array/Basic.lean#L38-L49","name":"Array.minD","line":38,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/Array/Basic.html#Array.